Surf_ENigma

This map is a surf style map(duhh), and some of the features are:

Main room, with spawns, platforms and such, where you're supposed to be able to keep surfing without stopping
Jail, where you end if you fail at surfing
Jail 2, where you can shoot or release teh prisoners from
Jail 3, where same as in jail2, just a tad safer than jail 2
I also added some secrets, but if i said them here, they wouldn't be secrets anymore, right? (^;*)
I used pretty damn long time on this, and i rly hope you like it as.. Well, it's my first map i actually cared to finish lol.

I think the deathmatch mod should fit in quite smoothly on this map, and the noblock mod would also be pretty handy some places.

Well this is the first readme i've ever written i think, and since i pretty much made the whole map myself, the Credits list wont be long :P.

Credits:
Pro...in mapping xD for fixing some technical problems
the rest of the members at eni.community.org for trying out my map, and just being kewl ^^

Well.. that was that, enjoy my map.
